E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('448','8','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">转眼间，2014年又过去了大半，商家们的年末促销又开始启动。网民们期盼的淘宝年终大促季也随着&ldquo;九九大促&rdquo;拉开了帷幕。随着房地产的不断升温，众多消费者之前购置的新房子都赶在年末前收楼，从而引发新一股装修热潮。作为家装必不可少的陶瓷行业又开始了新一轮的销售旺季。恰逢碰上淘宝年终大促季，哈德逊家居支招，教你如何网上选购质优价廉的</span></span><span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn/xwzx/qyxw/2014-08-27/414.html\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">家装瓷砖</span></span></a></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，希望为即将家装的你提供一点参考。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">由于淘宝年终大促的影响，网上</span></span><span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn/xwzx/qyxw/2014-08-28/419.html\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">瓷砖的价格</span></span></a></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">鱼龙混杂，很多莱鸟们对于家装瓷砖的挑选束手无策。面对庞大的淘宝市场，该从何入手呢？哈德逊家居认为，网上挑选瓷砖主要注意以下几点：</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">第一，看瓷砖的价格。消费者如果在网上挑选了较喜欢的瓷砖款式，可以通过瓷砖的型号搜索全网同型号产品。所有价格都一目了然，消费者选购的时候就比较清晰。千万不要受大促的影响选择过于便宜的。当然，有些品牌价格低但质量确实不错的，最好货比三家。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">第二，看买家对瓷砖的评价。因为是网购，我们不能触摸到实物，只能通过买家评价和产品详情去评定瓷砖质量的好坏。相对而言，天猫旗舰店的质量会好一些。挑选的时候可以适当选择天猫旗舰店。因为一些较出名的瓷砖品牌，他们的网店一般都是天猫旗舰店。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">第三，看网店的总体销量。一般网购瓷砖，如果该店的销量比较好的话，他家的瓷砖质量应该是性价比较高的。买家在网购的时候会考虑价格的同时也会要求质量。好像哈德逊瓷砖，网店的销量</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">连续几年全网第一</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，他家瓷砖的最大特点就是性价比较高，所以在网上的人气比较高。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">第四，看买家对售后服务的综合评价。如果网购瓷砖，在质量或者运输方面出现问题，好的售后服务有助于快速解决问题，并能在瓷砖使用过程中做到后续跟进。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">第五，购买前先上网查资料。网上搜一下比较</span></span><span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn/xwzx/qyxw/2014-08-31/430.html\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">知名的瓷砖品牌</span></span></a></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，有助于自己挑选和提供参考。挑选几款自己比较喜欢的款式，综合几个牌子，选择性价比较高的一款。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">在网购挑选质优价廉的瓷砖时，要耐心谨慎，不要贪图促销价格低。新家带给人温馨舒适的享受，挑选到合适的瓷砖对于提升新家幸福感有点缀作用。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p16\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 18pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊编辑原创</spa